TITLE: Implementing Resolver for Plaiceholder Plugin
DESCRIPTION: Example of implementing a resolver function in the Tailwind config to control how the plugin converts image paths to Buffers. This example reads files from a public directory.
SOURCE: https://github.com/joe-bell/plaiceholder/blob/main/docs/pages/docs/plugins/tailwind.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// @ts-check
import fs from "node:fs";
import path from "node:path";
import plaiceholder from "@plaiceholder/tailwindcss";

/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
export default {
  content: [],
  theme: {
    extend: {},
  },
  variants: {},
  plugins: [
    plaiceholder({
      resolver: (src) =>
        fs.readFileSync(path.join("./public", `${src}.jpg`)),
    }),
  ],
};
```

